Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.53,0:01:01.66,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Yomigaeru GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,You must seize the power!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.83,0:01:08.00,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kimi yo tsukame
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Fly toward the galaxy, Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.38,0:01:14.97,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Ginga e mukatte tobeyo GANDAMU
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam! Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.05,0:01:21.39,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Kidou senshi GANDAMU! GANDAMU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.13,0:01:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,The Federation sent a Medea squadron\Nto rescue the heavily damaged White Base...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.04,0:01:41.71,Default,,0,0,0,,...but the squadron was attacked\Nby Goufs and Dodai bombers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.57,0:01:48.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro and the others hurried to assist.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:52.35,Default,,0,0,0,,With the help of the G-Parts\Ndesigned to power-up the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.35,0:01:54.39,Default,,0,0,0,,...they succeeded in defeating the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.74,0:02:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Black Tri-Star
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.00,0:02:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a poor joke.\NThis plan is absolutely ridiculous!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.60,0:02:22.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you forgotten how many precious\Nresources M'Quve has sent us from under...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.50,0:02:24.17,Default,,0,0,0,,...the Earth Federation's siege?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.17,0:02:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, the practical\Napplication of mobile armor...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.68,0:02:30.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me. But the authority\Nof the military would be ruined.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.43,0:02:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A man's honor?! Military authority?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.95,0:02:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,These things can be sacrificed\Nfor Zeon victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.65,0:02:41.67,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll save your honor once we win this war.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.67,0:02:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Deliver the mobile suits for close combat\Non Earth to Commander Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.34,0:02:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,But, Your Highness, we can't do it right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.28,0:02:49.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course not!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.88,0:02:53.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Just get them to Char before\Nhe joins the Mad Angler squadron.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.76,0:02:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, I'm sure there are heavy mobile suits\Nallocated to other units...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.54,0:03:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,...that can be used for combat on Earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.23,0:03:02.30,Default,,0,0,0,,We should consider\Nsending those over too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.30,0:03:03.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Have you sent Doms to\Nthe Tri-Stars?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.82,0:03:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. They should have already left\Nsatellite orbit to rendezvous with M'Quve.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.20,0:03:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Good. Keep an eye on the situation\Nand respond accordingly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.12,0:03:19.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As the occupier of the Moon...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.52,0:03:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,...Kycilia could not join\Nthe battle on Earth in person.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.09,0:03:27.27,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting was unsettled on all fronts.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.27,0:03:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,The best she could do\Nwas to assist M'Quve...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:36.13,Default,,0,0,0,,...by sending her own brave warriors\Nknown as "Zeon's Tri-Stars".
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.21,0:04:01.04,Default,,0,0,0,,- Good morning.\N- Huh? G-Good morning, Lt. Matilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.04,0:04:03.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- What are these?\N- Components for the Gundam's\Npower-up parts.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.55,0:04:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have to do the repairs myself,\Nso I was organizing them.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.29,0:04:10.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- That's impressive.\N- Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.12,0:04:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,- Up to the bridge.\N- I'll show you the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.00,0:04:17.97,Default,,0,0,0,,- No, that's fine.\N- I'm pretty resourceful! I know a shortcut.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.97,0:04:19.63,Default,,0,0,0,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.58,0:04:32.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh. Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.44,0:04:33.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.83,0:04:35.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Amuro!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.08,0:04:36.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the big idea?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.32,0:04:37.90,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised me...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.90,0:04:41.03,Default,,0,0,0,,...you'd fix the air conditioner in my room\Nonce you finished breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.03,0:04:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.42,0:04:43.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.28,0:04:45.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hmph! Hmph! Hmph!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.37,0:04:46.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Quit it!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.20,0:04:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,That Ms. Matilda. She's just my type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.21,0:04:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,She's elegant. And she's so nice, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.64,0:04:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd be a happy man\Nif I had a girlfriend like Ms. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.09,0:04:58.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Idle hands make mischief.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.09,0:04:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.69,0:05:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah! Good morning! L-Lieutenant!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.82,0:05:05.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck finding an elegant girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.72,0:05:08.43,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Lieutenant!\NNow that I've made a total fool of myself...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I'd like to ask for permission to take\Na picture of you and myself!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.25,0:05:15.65,Default,,0,0,0,,No problem, as long as we do it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.65,0:05:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes! ...I'm honored!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.13,0:05:23.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Would you guys give me a break?!\NThis only gives me 12 copies per photo!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.78,0:05:26.41,Default,,0,0,0,,- C'mon, Kai!\N- Let me in, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.41,0:05:29.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm taking the picture! ...There!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.02,0:05:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Bright. I've brought Lt. Matilda to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.59,0:05:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.64,0:05:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Please don't get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.52,0:05:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm terribly sorry, Lieutenant.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.20,0:05:46.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You look better than I thought you would.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.77,0:05:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,All right!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.39,0:06:08.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our forces are progressing too slowly...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.93,0:06:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,...especially since I want to move up\NOperation Odessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.77,0:06:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Elran. Tell them to hurry and rendezvous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.21,0:06:15.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir! However...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.76,0:06:18.74,Default,,0,0,0,,"However"? In the military,\Nthere is only action. Isn't that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.74,0:06:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,- Sir!\N- General Revil.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.95,0:06:24.18,Default,,0,0,0,,An Air Force patrol team has sent us\Na report they caught.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.20,0:06:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,A Zeon Zanzibar warship\Nhas come down to Earth?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.20,0:06:32.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Our Big Tray has already\Nconfirmed that information.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.57,0:06:34.90,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Look at what it says after that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.90,0:06:38.97,Default,,0,0,0,,The Black Tri-Stars were dispatched\Nwith their new mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.97,0:06:42.89,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the ones who captured me\Nin the Battle of Loum.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.89,0:06:45.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're very tough.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.18,0:06:48.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got to begin Odessa Day earlier\Nthan we had anticipated. Right, Elran?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.39,0:06:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Yes, I'll inform\Nall units at once!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You're looking a bit pale.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.86,0:06:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Judock. You'd better not be spying\Nfor both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.05,0:07:02.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Revil is quite aware that the Black Tri-Stars\Nhave landed in a Zanzibar.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.19,0:07:05.31,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But that just can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:09.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Tell M'Quve that Operation Odessa\Nwill be commencing sooner.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.71,0:07:15.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Will we be able to finish\Nahead of schedule, Colonel?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.07,0:07:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... That's no problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.09,0:07:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,- Amuro. The Gundam's power-up parts.\N- Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:23.51,Default,,0,0,0,,- Ms. Matilda...\N- Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.51,0:07:25.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you join the Supply Corps?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.72,0:07:27.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.09,0:07:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Amid all the destruction of war...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.96,0:07:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,...it enables me to create things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.63,0:07:35.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Create things?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.97,0:07:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,While wars only bring destruction...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.06,0:07:45.94,Default,,0,0,0,,...I felt that human beings\Nneed more than that to go on living.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.83,0:07:48.98,Default,,0,0,0,,And we're clean now.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.51,0:07:55.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.70,0:08:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.72,0:08:03.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe that you're a strong person,\NMs. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.60,0:08:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,How cheeky.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.44,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.01,0:08:11.47,Default,,0,0,0,,It's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.53,0:08:21.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah! Leave them to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.35,0:08:24.23,Default,,0,0,0,,We're a whole different class than Char.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.23,0:08:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, show us the Trojan Horse\Nand this so-called white mobile suit.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.08,0:08:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, whatever...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.88,0:08:31.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega, Mash! Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.74,0:08:33.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.08,0:08:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,We're getting close.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.90,0:08:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,No metallic reaction detected...\NWe're jumping to the next mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.92,0:09:16.49,Default,,0,0,0,,- What is it?!\N- Enemy spotted. 3 mobile suits...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.49,0:09:18.51,Default,,0,0,0,,...approaching from 2 o'clock.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.51,0:09:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Prepare to intercept. Mirai, take charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.25,0:09:22.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.42,0:09:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,- It's the enemy!\N- The enemy's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.84,0:09:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,All right! All clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.80,0:09:28.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Move Medea No. 3 out of\Nthe White Base's path!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.39,0:09:33.70,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad the controls are up here now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.70,0:09:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,But can I really operate this by myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.60,0:09:38.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Hayato! Are you all right there?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,If you can work yours by yourself,\NMr. Kai, then I'll be fine too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.90,0:09:51.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're past our second surveillance net.\NThey're moving quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.14,0:09:52.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Is the Gundam ready to go yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.83,0:09:55.58,Default,,0,0,0,,That's the problem...\NThey're still checking the G-Armor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.58,0:09:58.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I was just told they need me down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.00,0:09:59.25,Default,,0,0,0,,By whom?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.25,0:10:02.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Engineering Colonel Seki.\NHe wants me to operate the G-Fighter.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.39,0:10:06.09,Default,,0,0,0,,What?! Can't Job John do it?\NHe's a pilot too.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.09,0:10:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I have experience with mobile suits.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.18,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Let's have Fraw Bow\Ntake over your position for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.93,0:10:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Mirai!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.93,0:10:16.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine's just been overhauled.\NDon't forget to do a trial run.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.70,0:10:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Understood!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.81,0:10:19.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, Fraw Bow. Please take over.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.77,0:10:20.94,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm off.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.61,0:10:28.70,Default,,0,0,0,,The computer takes care of the connection,\Nso the pilot doesn't have to worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.70,0:10:30.78,Default,,0,0,0,,But what if the computer gets damaged?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.78,0:10:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,If the laser sensors are synchronized,\Nit's possible to dock manually.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.21,0:10:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But you'll stall if your speed\Nis under 600 km/h.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.89,0:10:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the G-Fighter pilot?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.02,0:10:42.21,Default,,0,0,0,,- She's here!\N- Hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.21,0:10:43.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah, yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.61,0:10:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This isn't the G-Fighter.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I believe It's the G-Armor.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.33,0:10:55.35,Default,,0,0,0,,- Can I handle this one?\N- For someone who's piloted the Gundam...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.35,0:10:57.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...it'll be a piece of cake.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.44,0:10:59.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Just rely on the machinery.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.66,0:11:01.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be watching you from the bridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.44,0:11:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, ma'am. See ya later.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.34,0:11:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla! Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.12,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm still not finished checking. Hold on.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.60,0:11:15.50,Default,,0,0,0,,These guys are fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.06,0:11:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,The engine output won't increase.\NEven if we manage to take off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.37,0:11:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,- Should we have a specialist check it out?\N- Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.93,0:11:30.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! Please ask Lieutenant Matilda\Nand Colonel Seki to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.37,0:11:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, White Base?\NWhy haven't you taken off?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.19,0:11:36.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The main engine output won't increase.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.61,0:11:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Colonel!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.40,0:11:41.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow! How are Amuro and Sayla\Ndoing with the G-Armor?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.40,0:11:43.55,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like Sayla's having trouble with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.55,0:11:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She can't figure out\Nthe docking process with Gundam!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.92,0:11:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,No time. Tell her to leave it to Amuro,\Nand just take off...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.04,0:11:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Ah...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.95,0:11:53.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine. Please allow the G-Armor to take off.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.37,0:11:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes... G-Armor. Amuro and Sayla, launch.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.21,0:11:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Right! Amuro, Ms. Sayla, please take off!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.34,0:12:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,These are for docking...\NFirst, then second...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.42,0:12:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Ms. Sayla! We're going!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.18,0:12:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! Go ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.69,0:12:08.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Engines at max! Align takeoff axis! Ready?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.64,0:12:09.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.69,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.20,0:12:28.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.08,0:12:30.91,Default,,0,0,0,,To my left?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.02,0:12:35.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Gotcha!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.51,0:12:43.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Incoming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.13,0:13:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Ms. Sayla! Left!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.52,0:13:14.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.71,0:13:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,In G-Armor mode, your cockpit\Nhas better control of the aircraft!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.11,0:13:20.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You can do it!\NIs the infrared monitor ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.93,0:13:23.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll be firing the G-Armor's main cannons!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.70,0:13:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Where's the enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.71,0:13:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,They're behind us! Turn us around!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.72,0:13:30.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}- Roger!\N- You've gotta pull It harder!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.79,0:13:33.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Step on the pedal with all your might!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.88,0:13:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.91,0:13:47.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is tricky.\NIt's bigger, so it's much harder to turn...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.29,0:13:50.42,Default,,0,0,0,,But the G-Armor's beam cannon power\Nlasts three times longer...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.42,0:13:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,...than the Gundam's. We've got to...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.63,0:13:54.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Rotate left, 90 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.80,0:13:56.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm aiming the beam cannons.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.71,0:13:57.82,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Roger!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.82,0:13:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Proceed at a 40 degree angle!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.20,0:14:04.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay. Take this!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.99,0:14:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll swat you, you pesky fly!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.84,0:14:17.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I've never seen that one before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.90,0:14:20.07,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not in the Trojan Horse's data, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.22,0:14:27.75,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a fighter-bomber,\Nbut I've never seen that silhouette before.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.06,0:14:32.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Firing rear missiles,\Nangle minus 4 degrees!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.57,0:14:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,N-Not bad, you mysterious fighter!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.86,0:14:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no problem with\Nthe synchro-motor in itself? That's odd.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.72,0:14:45.31,Default,,0,0,0,,- No problem here either.\N- Check it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.14,Default,,0,0,0,,The G-Armor's having trouble in combat.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.14,0:14:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Both Guncannon and Guntank\Nare being forced back!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.69,0:14:50.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Lieutenant Matilda!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.98,0:14:53.32,Default,,0,0,0,,It'll be fine. We can count on Colonel Seki.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.79,0:14:55.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Fraw Bow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.04,0:14:58.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Please have my Medea ready\Nfor takeoff at any time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.69,0:14:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.51,0:15:03.07,Default,,0,0,0,,We may be just a bit too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.07,0:15:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,And what makes you think that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.96,0:15:07.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No particular reason. I somehow feel it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.85,0:15:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.23,0:15:13.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Nothing, ma'am.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.32,0:15:19.89,Default,,0,0,0,,You seem to be a chronic worrier.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.74,0:15:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,I suppose I am.\NPeople do tell me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.81,0:15:28.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Amuro. Sayla. Kai. Hayato.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.13,0:15:32.82,Default,,0,0,0,,There it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.97,0:15:39.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm such a useless klutz!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.62,0:15:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't even slow the enemy down.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.41,0:15:44.96,Default,,0,0,0,,He's tough!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.11,0:15:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Sayla!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.34,0:15:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm okay! Where are they?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:16:00.60,Default,,0,0,0,,They've advanced pretty far now.\NPlease hide us behind the mountain!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.60,0:16:02.66,Default,,0,0,0,,- You're converting to the Gundam?\N- Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:04.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I be able to dock the parts?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.77,0:16:06.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I know you can, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.41,0:16:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what you've always\Nsaid to me, Ms. Sayla.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.01,0:16:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're returning the favor?\NThen I'll give it a try, Amuro.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.55,0:16:18.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Pattern G automatic set.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.01,0:16:21.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If there's any problem, I will...\NNo, it'll be just fine! We'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.40,0:16:31.05,Default,,0,0,0,,4... 3... 2...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.05,0:16:32.97,Default,,0,0,0,,...1... 0.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is everything okay, Ms. Sayla?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.46,0:16:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, the computer did it all for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.03,0:16:50.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, Amuro! Hurry back to the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.53,0:16:51.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Roger!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.30,0:16:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,What? There's a Medea!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.85,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not Ms. Matilda's Medea, is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.08,0:17:05.34,Default,,0,0,0,,The pressure has increased\Nin No. 2 and No. 3.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.34,0:17:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The rest are no good. In fact,\Nthe pressure seems to be decreasing.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.01,0:17:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}We figured out the problem!\i\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.19,0:17:12.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Please finish it in two minutes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.41,0:17:21.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Fire main cannons!\NFire front missiles horizontally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.08,0:17:23.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile suits?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.75,0:17:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Found you! I'm putting an end to this!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.47,0:17:38.71,Default,,0,0,0,,He dodged my shot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.10,0:17:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The vulcans have no effect?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.52,0:17:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! They've reached the White Base!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.15,0:17:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,This Federation mobile suit!\NIt's not as great as they say!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.33,0:18:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,We're this close to making\Nthe White Base survive this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.21,0:18:09.99,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't sit around and watch it be destroyed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.51,0:18:13.87,Default,,0,0,0,,- Take off! Hurry!\N- Huh? Yes, ma'am!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.14,0:18:23.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! That mobile suit is planning\Nto destroy the White Base first!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.90,0:18:27.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That pilot is no regular guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.90,0:18:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Ortega! Mash!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.22,0:18:32.51,Default,,0,0,0,,We're gonna pull a Jet Stream Attack\Non that mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.83,0:18:39.94,Default,,0,0,0,,He's quicker than I thought. Ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.94,0:18:41.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.75,0:18:44.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Is he... coming at me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.27,0:19:06.63,Default,,0,0,0,,It's working! Let's do the Jet Stream Attack\None more time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.11,0:19:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? A Medea? But who's on board?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.45,0:19:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,They're coming...!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.31,0:19:21.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.67,0:19:29.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He used me as a springboard?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.56,0:19:40.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Drive that Dom into the ground!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.42,0:19:46.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Why you...! We almost had that mobile suit!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.90,0:20:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I couldn't do anything to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.57,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Mash's Dom... destroyed...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.37,0:20:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,That mobile suit slipped\Npast our Jet Stream Attack...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.48,0:20:33.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.81,0:20:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,No weapons left.\NWe need to rethink our tactics, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.81,0:20:56.35,Default,,0,0,0,,We've got good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.35,0:20:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The White Base repulsed\NZeon's Black Tri-Stars.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.67,0:21:01.67,Default,,0,0,0,,It's back on the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.67,0:21:04.89,Default,,0,0,0,,l-ls that so? ...Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.89,0:21:09.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, how about that White Base.\NIt's proven to be the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.28,0:21:13.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}That crew...?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.16,0:21:15.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Where do they get their strength from?!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.96,0:21:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Elran.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.62,0:21:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.69,0:21:21.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Operation Odessa,\Nthe attack on M'Quve's base.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.20,0:21:23.87,Default,,0,0,0,,It begins at 0600 hours today.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:33.81,0:21:35.42,Default,,0,0,0,,To express our sorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.42,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,...for the fallen members of Matilda's\NMedea transport squadron...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All hands! ...Salute!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.94,0:22:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,This is all because of my inexperience...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry, Ms. Matilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.06,0:22:48.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.18,0:22:51.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.56,0:22:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.31,0:22:56.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.77,0:22:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.20,0:23:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Matilda!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:05.70,0:23:09.23,Default,,0,0,0,,MS. MATILDA!!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.21,0:23:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Before Operation Odessa begins...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.24,0:23:24.04,Default,,0,0,0,,...the traitors are discovered and arrested,\Nleading the Earth Federation to victory.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.04,0:23:29.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But the two surviving Black Tri-Star Doms\Nattack the Gundam relentlessly...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:29.82,0:23:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,...determined to avenge their fallen comrade.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.80,0:23:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Mobile Suit Gundam. Next episode...\NThe Battle of Odessa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.39,0:23:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,The Battle of Odessa
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.80,0:23:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Will you be able to survive?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The star shining far off in space...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, it's your homeland\Nwhere you were born
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Do you remember the days\Nof your childhood?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,The morning when you woke up in warmth?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Amuro, do not look back, Amuro...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,A man must hide his tears, hide his tears
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics Top,,0,0,0,,Only look to tomorrow, to tomorrow\NForever...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.69,0:23:54.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Furimukanaide
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.53,0:23:59.53,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Uchuu no kanata ni kagayaku hoshi ha
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.53,0:24:09.75,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, Omae no umareta furusato da
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.75,0:24:14.68,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Oboeteirukai, Shounen no hi no koto wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:14.68,0:24:19.31,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Atatakai nukumori no nake de mezameta asa wo
Dialogue: 0,0:24:19.31,0:24:24.69,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Amuro, furimukanaide na, Amuro
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.69,0:24:29.27,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Otoko ha namida wo misenu mono, Misenu mono
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.27,0:24:39.58,Lyrics,,0,0,0,,Tada ashita e to ashita e to, Eien ni...
